    <p>This site is dedicated to helping you unlock your e-reader’s full potential safely and responsibly through jailbreaking.</p>

    <h3>What You’ll Learn:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>How to jailbreak popular e-readers like Kindle, Kobo, and PocketBook</li>
      <li>Installing advanced reading apps like KOReader for enhanced reading experience</li>
      <li>Customizing fonts, margins, layouts, and other display options</li>
      <li>Accessing a wider range of e-book formats and features</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>What to Know First:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Jailbreaking may void your warranty and carries some risks</li>
      <li>Our step-by-step guides minimize risks and simplify the process</li>
      <li>This project is for curious, careful readers who want more control</li>
      <li>Always back up your data before attempting a jailbreak</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Start exploring by selecting a topic from the navigation on the left.</p>
  </div>
</SplitLayout>
